    "Step 9: Privacy and Legal Compliance.",
    "Ensure that the entire process complies with data privacy laws and regulations, obtain necessary permissions, and protect personal and sensitive information in the data.",
    "Step 10: Maintenance and Updates.",
    "Regularly maintain the data collection system to ensure the continuous updating of data.",
    "Consider replacing with new data sources and collection strategies as needed."
